// VERIFICATION 4 — None type fatal error (outside attempt block)
// Sets .myval to none, then tries to add it to a number.
// Execution must halt with a fatal error.
// The error log must be written and must identify the bad operation.

show "Setting .myval to none ..."
set .myval to none

show "About to add none to 10 — this should be fatal ..."
set .result to .myval + 10

// These lines must NOT be reached:
show "THIS LINE SHOULD NOT APPEAR"
show .result
